{
  "id": "67eb41600f6d1d1d0b093565",
  "title": "〇〇込み (数学)",
  "created": 1743470946,
  "updated": 1743472117,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "67eb41600f6d1d1d0b093565",
      "text": "〇〇込み (数学)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743470946,
      "updated": 1743470946
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43ca0000000000ff3ac0",
      "text": "#教えてGPT",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471562,
      "updated": 1743471576
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43cb0000000000ff3ac1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471562,
      "updated": 1743471562
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430e0000000000ff3a75",
      "text": "[埋め込み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471453
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a77",
      "text": " 用いられる分野:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471408
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a79",
      "text": "  [数学]: [位相空間論]、微分幾何学",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471466
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a7b",
      "text": "  [物理学]: [理論物理]、[弦理論]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471463
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a7d",
      "text": "  [工学]: [コンピュータグラフィックス]、[データ解析]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471473
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a7f",
      "text": " 意味:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471692
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb444c0000000000ff3ac2",
      "text": "  直感: 一つの構造を別の構造の内部に自然に配置する操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471692,
      "updated": 1743471699
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44540000000000ff3ac3",
      "text": "  数学: 単射かつ構造保存な写像 f: X → Y により、対象 X を Y の部分対象として同一視する操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471700,
      "updated": 1743471703
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43530000000000ff3ab8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471443,
      "updated": 1743471443
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43530000000000ff3ab9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471443,
      "updated": 1743471443
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a81",
      "text": "[はめ込み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471482
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a83",
      "text": " 用いられる分野:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471410
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a85",
      "text": "  [数学]: [集合論]、[位相空間論]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471490
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a87",
      "text": "  [物理学]: 一部の理論モデル",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471524
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a89",
      "text": "  [工学]: [システム統合]、[設計手法]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471531
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a8b",
      "text": " 意味: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471530,
      "updated": 1743471708
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb445c0000000000ff3ac4",
      "text": " \t直感: 対象を既存の枠組みに適合させて配置する操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471708,
      "updated": 1743471711
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44710000000000ff3ac6",
      "text": " \t数学: 与えられた対象 X を、構造や性質を保持する写像 f: X → Y を通して Y 内に収める操作。文脈により条件が異なる場合がある。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471728,
      "updated": 1743471779
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43540000000000ff3abb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471444,
      "updated": 1743471444
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44720000000000ff3ac7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471729,
      "updated": 1743471729
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43400000000000ff3ab2",
      "text": "[組み込み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471424,
      "updated": 1743472013
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43400000000000ff3ab3",
      "text": " 用いられる分野:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471424,
      "updated": 1743471424
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43400000000000ff3ab4",
      "text": "  [数学]: [位相論]、[線形代数]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471424,
      "updated": 1743471546
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43400000000000ff3ab5",
      "text": "  [物理学]: [理論物理]のモデル構築",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471424,
      "updated": 1743471552
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43400000000000ff3ab6",
      "text": "  [工学]: [機械学習]、[データ表現]、[システム設計]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471424,
      "updated": 1743471557
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43400000000000ff3ab7",
      "text": " 意味: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471424,
      "updated": 1743471761
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44920000000000ff3acf",
      "text": " \t直感: 一つの対象を別の大きな体系内に自然に収める方法。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471761,
      "updated": 1743471761
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44950000000000ff3ad0",
      "text": " \t数学: 対象 X を、単射かつ構造保存な写像を介して他の対象 Y の部分として内包する操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471764,
      "updated": 1743471805
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43560000000000ff3abc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471446,
      "updated": 1743471446
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3ad2",
      "text": "[繰り込み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472034,
      "updated": 1743472041
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3ad4",
      "text": " 用いられる分野:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472035,
      "updated": 1743472081
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3ad6",
      "text": "  数学: 数学物理、解析学（発散の制御に関する手法）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472035,
      "updated": 1743472081
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3ad8",
      "text": "  物理学: 量子場理論、統計力学",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472035,
      "updated": 1743472081
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3ada",
      "text": "  工学: 物理シミュレーション（例: 電磁界解析）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472035,
      "updated": 1743472081
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45c10000000000ff3ae1",
      "text": " 意味:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472064,
      "updated": 1743472082
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3adc",
      "text": "  直感: 物理計算で現れる無限大の項を、実際の観測値に合わせるため、理論内のパラメータ（例えば質量や結合定数）を再定義する手法。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472035,
      "updated": 1743472099
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45e30000000000ff3ae2",
      "text": "  計算上の「おかしな無限大」を、現実的な有限の値に置き換えるプロセス。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472099,
      "updated": 1743472104
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45a30000000000ff3adf",
      "text": "  数学: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472035,
      "updated": 1743472117
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45f50000000000ff3ae4",
      "text": "   発散項を含む作用や伝播関数に対して、まず正則化により発散を一時的に制御し、次に適切なカウンター項を導入して局所性や共変性を保持しつつ再定義を行う操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472117,
      "updated": 1743472117
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb45f10000000000ff3ae3",
      "text": "   これにより、スケール変換下での不変性条件を満たしながら、有限な物理量を厳密に定義する枠組みが構築されます。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743472113,
      "updated": 1743472114
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43560000000000ff3abd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471446,
      "updated": 1743471446
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a8d",
      "text": "[畳み込み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743472016
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a8f",
      "text": " 用いられる分野:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471412
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a91",
      "text": "  [数学]: [解析学]、[確率論]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471607
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a93",
      "text": "  [物理学]: 信号の[応答解析]、[統計力学]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471621
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a95",
      "text": "  [工学]: [信号処理]、[画像処理]、[制御工学]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471615
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3a97",
      "text": " 意味: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471734
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44770000000000ff3ac9",
      "text": " \t直感: 2つの関数やデータを結合して新たな関数や応答を生成する操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471734,
      "updated": 1743471734
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44790000000000ff3aca",
      "text": " \t数学: 関数 f と g に対して、(f * g)(x) = ∫ f(y) g(x − y) dy（または離散和）という形で定義される、二項演算。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471736,
      "updated": 1743471810
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43580000000000ff3abe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471448,
      "updated": 1743471448
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb43580000000000ff3abf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471448,
      "updated": 1743471448
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3aa5",
      "text": "[逆畳み込み]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743472020
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3aa7",
      "text": " 用いられる分野:",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471419
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3aa9",
      "text": "  [数学]: [解析学]、[関数解析]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471642
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3aab",
      "text": "  [物理学]: [画像再構築]、[天体観測]データの解析",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471647
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3aad",
      "text": "  [工学]: [信号処理]、[医用画像解析]、[制御システム]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471656
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb430f0000000000ff3aaf",
      "text": " 意味: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471374,
      "updated": 1743471740
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb447d0000000000ff3acc",
      "text": " \t直感: [畳み込み]操作で合成されたデータから、元の信号や関数を復元する逆の操作。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471741,
      "updated": 1743471741
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb44890000000000ff3acd",
      "text": " \t数学: 畳み込み演算 f * g において、既知の g と f * g から元の f を再構成する、逆問題を解く手法。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471753,
      "updated": 1743471819
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb433c0000000000ff3ab0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471420,
      "updated": 1743471420
    },
    {
      "id": "67eb433d0000000000ff3ab1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1743471420,
      "updated": 1743471420
    }
  ]
}